After I'm gone,

9
00:00:38,360 --> 00:00:41,080
you can't just rely

10
00:00:41,080 --> 00:00:46,840
on your sister and Bao.

11
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:51,040
You need to learn

12
00:00:51,040 --> 00:00:54,360
to be a responsible man.

13
00:00:57,160 --> 00:00:58,400
The police force

14
