19
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,280
Bin.

20
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,680
Dad.

21
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,920
Promise me

22
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:33,240
you will

23
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:37,520
